==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[ki-]]'' (interrogative and relative [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-om]]'' (correlative suffix of quantity)

===Correlative===
'''kiom'''

# [[how much]] (interrogative and relative correlative of quantity)
#: Like other interrogative and relative correlatives, '''kiom''' can be combined with ''[[ajn]]'', the adverbial particle of generality. '''''Kiom''' ajn'' thus means ''however much''.

